      <title>Jane Street 重返债务市场，获得 10 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-returns-to-debt-markets-with-1-billion-loan-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周一的一连串交易中，Jane Street Group LLC 推出了一笔 10 亿美元的杠杆贷款，重返杠杆债务市场。]]></description>
