    <item>
      <title>美联储博斯蒂克表示，12 月利率决议仍有“选择余地”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/fed-s-bostic-keeping-options-open-for-december-rate-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚特兰大联邦储备银行行长拉斐尔博斯蒂克表示，他尚未决定本月是否需要降息，但仍认为官员们应该在未来几个月继续降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/fed-s-bostic-keeping-options-open-for-december-rate-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃莱克特拉股价暴跌，萨利纳斯一天将损失 40 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在监管机构下令交易所在停牌数月后恢复交易后，Grupo Elektra 股价周一暴跌逾 60%，亿万富翁里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 的财富因此蒸发约 40 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储发言人称市场为大数据周做准备，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待本周的大量经济数据和美联储官员讲话，美国国债周一缩减早盘跌幅，这些讲话可能会决定本月晚些时候央行政策决定的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
